'''新幾內亞大鼠屬'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Anisomys''），是[[囓齒目|囓齒目]][[鼠科|鼠科]]的一個[[屬|屬]]，本屬為[[單型|單型]]屬，僅包含'''新幾內亞大鼠'''（學名：''Anisomys imitator''）一種物種，分布於[[新幾內亞|新幾內亞]]島上的{{le|新幾內亞高地|New Guinea Highlands}}海拔1200–3500公尺處<ref name=IUCN/>。

新幾內亞大鼠在當地{{le|卡拉姆語|Kalam language}}中被稱為「gudi-ws」<ref name="Kalam-Pawley">Pawley, Andrew and Ralph Bulmer. 2011. ''A Dictionary of Kalam with Ethnographic Notes''. Canberra. Pacific Linguistics.</ref>，會以{{le|卡魯卡樹|Pandanus julianettii}}的核果為食<ref name="Stilltoe">{{cite book |last1=Stilltoe |first1=Paul |title=Roots of the Earth:  Crops in the Highlands of Papua New Guinea |date=1983 |publisher=Manchester university Press |location=Manchester, UK |isbn=978-0-7190-0874-0 |language=en |oclc=9556314 |lccn=82-62247}}</ref>，因此當地種植此樹的農民會在樹幹上設置障礙物以阻止其取食<ref name="Stilltoe" /><ref name="French">{{cite book |last1=French |first1=Bruce R. |title=Growing food in the Southern Highlands Province of Papua New Guinea |date=1982 |publisher=AFTSEMU (Agricultural Field Trials, Surveys, Evaluation and Monitoring Unit) of the World Bank funded project in the Southern Highlands of Papua New Guinea |pages=64 – 71 |url=https://docplayer.net/42672690-Growing-food-in-the-southern-highlands-province-of-papua-new-guinea-bruce-r-french.html |accessdate=20 September 2018 |format=PDF |archive-date=2018-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181030035515/https://docplayer.net/42672690-Growing-food-in-the-southern-highlands-province-of-papua-new-guinea-bruce-r-french.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另外新幾內亞大鼠也是當地人打獵的獵物之一<ref name=IUCN/>。

